      "writtenOn": "2026-03-16T17:12:29Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I couldn\u0027t find any malloc-mocking infrastructure (e.g., __wrap_malloc or similar) in this project to inject allocation failures in a test and adding that would be a broader effort beyond this fix. I\u0027ve added *size \u003d 0 on the failure path so callers can\u0027t misuse a stale size value — that\u0027s the observable behavior a test would verify.",
      "parentUuid": "38761d25_4f99f9ea",
      "revId": "2d668bf94b9e65b0b94433721a4639249648d907",
